27:32.040 --> 27:35.400
Vince, you've saved the day.
Thank you, child.

27:35.440 --> 27:37.520
I'm glad that everyone is
reconciled.

27:37.560 --> 27:39.480
I thought I was goner.
No way, Pops.

27:39.520 --> 27:42.040
Let's lock him in his room
and call the cops.

