Can someone tell me
what's gone on today?

27:50.520 --> 27:52.760
It's more than a rhyming
couplet can relay.

27:54.440 --> 27:56.960
I wish you had your diamond ring.

27:57.000 --> 27:58.640
But, hush!

27:58.680 --> 28:00.240
I think that I did hear
a toilet flush.

28:04.880 --> 28:06.240
Oh!

28:06.280 --> 28:07.320
You found it.

28:13.440 --> 28:15.000
Aw!

28:16.880 --> 28:19.000
SMATTERING OF APPLAUSE

28:24.280 --> 28:26.640
I hope you've enjoyed
your stay at Zanzibar.

28:26.680 --> 28:28.880
We're all little older,
if not wiser.

28:28.920 --> 28:31.640
If you've enjoyed your stay,
please, tell your friends.

28:31.680 --> 28:33.680
And write a nice review
on TripAdvisor!

